# LDCPortfolio Project Rule

This repository is a personal portfolio web application focused on an interactive and modern user experience.

## Project Purpose

- Present personal profile content in structured sections (hero, about, skills, projects, contact, footer).
- Deliver a polished front-end experience with animation, theme switching, and bilingual content.
- Keep implementation simple and maintainable for iterative UI updates.

## Core Technology Stack

- Frontend: React 19 + TypeScript.
- Build tool: Vite 7.
- Styling: Tailwind CSS 3 with utility-first styling and custom CSS variables.
- UI primitives: Radix UI + shadcn-style component structure in `src/components/ui`.
- Animation: Framer Motion.
- Internationalization: i18next + react-i18next with English and Vietnamese locales.

## Working Conventions

- Treat this as a frontend-only static app unless the user explicitly asks to add backend services.
- Prefer updates inside existing section/component/context structure before introducing new architecture.
- Reuse existing UI components in `src/components/ui` instead of rebuilding primitives.
- Keep user-facing text translatable and synchronized across locale files.

